By Mr. Moore, a petition (accompanied by bill, Senate, No. 1414) of Michael O. Moore, John J.
Cronin, James B. Eldridge, Paul R. Feeney and other members of the Senate for legislation to
increase access to Applied Behavior Analysis services by recognizing assistant level providers.
